who is judged in this case?
who has been condemned?
the hypo- thetical syllogism, or the man who has been deceived by it ?
Does he then who has the power of making any de- claration about you know what is pious or impious ?
Has he studied it, and has he learned it ?
Where ?
From whom ?
Then is it the fact that a musician pays no regard to him who declares that the lowest 20 chord in the lyre is the highest;
