and shall he who is really instructed pay any regard to the uninstructed man when he pronounces judgment on what is pious and what is impious, on what is just and unjust?
Oh, the signal wrong done by the instructed.
Did they learn this here ?
21Will you not leave the small arguments (λογάια)22 about these matters to others, to lazy fellows, that they may sit in a corner and receive their sorry pay, or grumble that no one gives them any thing;
