As soon as you go out in the morning, examine every man whom you see, every man whom you hear;
answer as to a question, What have you seen?
A handsome man or .woman ?
Apply the rule.
Is this independent of the will, or dependent ?
Independent.
Take it away.
What have you seen ?
A man lamenting over the death of a child.
Apply the rule.
Death is a thing independent of the will.
Take it away.
Has the proconsul met you ?
Apply the rule.
What kind of thing is a proconsul's office?
Independent of the will, or dependent on it ?
Independent.
Take this away also:
it does not stand examination :
cast it away :
it is nothing to you.
